title: Episode 153: Tainted-Love (Feat. Tony Rock)
itunes:title: Episode 153: Tainted-Love (Feat. Tony Rock)
description:
Comedian Tony Rock joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and things get wild when he explains why he purchased multiple cars for his previous girlfriends. Tony goes on to share his first time having sex, how to use makeshift condoms, and much more. Enjoy!
